# Per-repo extra hash-pin patterns for audit-harness (read by harness-hash.sh).
#
# This repo is a GitHub Action shell with no .feature files and no coverage-
# threshold config files (.c8rc.json / stryker.conf.json), so the harness'
# default canonical patterns pin nothing here. The policy-enforcement surface
# that MUST be tamper-evident in this repo is:
#
#   - action.yml        the gate's I/O contract (inputs/outputs/runs) — the
#                       behavioral spec a consumer depends on
#   - tests/TESTING.md  the testing policy (coverage floor + gate list) that
#                       escape-scan reads; a silent edit here is an escape attempt
#
# An edit to either without a paired `audit-harness init` is flagged
# HARNESS_TAMPERED by `audit-harness verify` in CI.
action.yml
tests/TESTING.md
